name: Worlds are born in silence
description:
Drawing combined with digital lines

To reach the inner spaces from which whole worlds can emerge, one passes through the portals opened by silence. One dives deep to where general language cannot breathe or flies to the edges of the world, throwing synapses into abyss - hoping for a new kind of sign. Monolingual syntax of inner self in silence may not be intelligible in the general, but it is recognizable as a sign in the universal.
